Sigma0 : public yes /0 no /0 a /0 b /0 i /0 s /0

Transaction ReceivePrivateKey :
send inv ( pk ( i ) ) . nil

Transaction Server :
* x in {a ,b , i }.
* y in { yes , no }.
receive M .
try N := dcrypt ( inv ( pk ( s ) ) ,M ) in
    if y = yes then
        new R .
        send crypt ( pk ( x ) , pair ( yes , N ) ,R ) . nil
    else
        new R .
        send crypt ( pk ( x ) ,no , R ) . nil
catch nil

Bound : 2